{"tid":1468404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[錯就要認]對唔住 我哋阻止唔到臥底衝擊旅客","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:33:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T19:28:53.000Z","uid":232190,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5379e90b785b5ac2b31220127f477ac9767bde9a","tid":1468404,"uid":232190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:33:19.000Z","msg":"我哋明白，每個人嘅安全十分重要，特別係由世界各地訪港嘅人，我哋要盡最大努力令佢哋對香港有個美好回憶。<br />\n手無寸鐵 弱質纖纖嘅我哋又點能輕易制止一個又一個久經訓練嘅臥底？<br />\n不完善，所以我哋會向旅客道歉，並好好檢討，審慎商討以後嘅集會。<br />\n聽日(8月14日)，機場道歉日。<br />\n用微小嘅力量作出真摯嘅道歉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c06808193a552e9a57a4f70d7ee50ae115daf77","tid":1468404,"uid":232190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:35:13.000Z","msg":"自推下"},{"pid":"72e5b956eeae61b2e6f037fd1a3d8c25aade2e2c","tid":1468404,"uid":141976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23e0906e8294480cba038f140520e99cafb94d7","tid":1468404,"uid":232190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:36:24.000Z","msg":"認同幫推<br />\n<br />\n721  811"},{"pid":"c25b348ea704239a161d4fa487b66383b6c3ecd3","tid":1468404,"uid":232190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:37:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2efcd2f6a2fa85315d4d8c78dba2165e09feee","tid":1468404,"uid":232190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed93550106257dc349c91cbd22916bab163e89ba","tid":1468404,"uid":43413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0172eb9c3d6b19e47cb093d02ac117d97f6a7ce9","tid":1468404,"uid":23672,